Author: IDKijustdrinkhere
Text: Here’s the thing. Idk how old you are, but young people are stupid and have aspirations that everything including their mental health and the mental health of someone they are with forever is top notch. Reality is, being an adult sucks and literally no one is perfect. My point is, he’s too young and still a dumbass.  Ps. I hope you feel better soon and it’s not you it’s them.
